---
import { MapPin, Car, Footprints, Check, X, ArrowRight, Clock, Mountain, Home } from 'lucide-react';
---

<div class="min-h-screen bg-[#F5F2ED] text-[#1A1A1A] font-sans selection:bg-[#1A1A1A] selection:text-[#F5F2ED]">
  
  {/* 1. HERO / EDITORIAL SPLIT */}
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-end mb-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-[#666] mb-6 block">
          Location Authority • Frigiliana
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[6rem] leading-[0.95] tracking-tight">
          The Reality of <br class="hidden md:block" />
          Arrival
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 pb-2">
        <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Frigiliana is not a flat coastal resort. It is vertical, stepped, and historic. 
          Here, the parking question is really a question about your daily movement rhythm.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="h-px w-full bg-[#1A1A1A] opacity-10"></div>
  </section>

  {/* 2. THE SHORT ANSWER (DECISION BLOCK) */}
  <section class="py-12 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight">
          Is it difficult <br/> with a car?
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4 border-b border-[#1A1A1A]/10 pb-2">
            The Short Answer
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light leading-relaxed">
            It is not inherently difficult, but it is <em>different</em>. Frigiliana rewards those who prioritize atmosphere over zero-friction, door-to-door car access.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4 border-b border-[#1A1A1A]/10 pb-2">
            The Real Variable
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light leading-relaxed">
            The experience depends entirely on <strong>where you stay</strong>. A house at the very top of the old town feels completely different from a stay in the lower village.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 3. PARKING IN PRACTICE (GRID) */}
  <section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white border border-[#E5E5E5] rounded-[24px] p-8 md:p-16">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-6">What Matters Most</h2>
        <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-lg">
          Forget the mythology of "impossible parking." Focus on these three practical realities instead.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F5F2ED] flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <MapPin class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1A1A1A]" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-lg">Position Over Proximity</h3>
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            The absolute nearest parking space matters less than the steepness of the walk. A slightly longer flat walk is always better than a short, vertical climb with luggage.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F5F2ED] flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <Clock class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1A1A1A]" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-lg">The Daily Rhythm</h3>
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Midday is dense with day-trippers. Early mornings and evenings are calm. If your stay is a base for constant midday in-and-out driving, you will feel more friction.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F5F2ED] flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <Footprints class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1A1A1A]" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-lg">The Walking Reality</h3>
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            You will walk. You will climb stairs. Frigiliana is a pedestrian-first environment. Embrace this as part of the charm, not a logistical failure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 4. STAY MODELS (COMPARISON) */}
  <section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-4">The Stay Models</h2>
        <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-lg max-w-xl">
          How your choice of location dictates your daily movement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {/* Model 1 */}
      <div class="border border-[#E5E5E5] bg-white p-8 flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <Mountain class="w-6 h-6 text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2">High Old Town</h3>
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm">Maximum atmosphere, maximum effort.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto space-y-4">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-t border-[#E5E5E5] pt-4">
            <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[#666]">Friction</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium">High</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-t border-[#E5E5E5] pt-4">
            <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[#666]">Car Access</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium">None (Walk only)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Model 2 */}
      <div class="border border-[#1A1A1A] bg-[#1A1A1A] text-white p-8 flex flex-col h-full relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-white text-[#1A1A1A] text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 m-4">
          The Balance
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <Home class="w-6 h-6 text-white mb-4" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2">Lower Village</h3>
          <p class="text-[#A0A0A0] font-light text-sm">Historic character without the extreme climb.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto space-y-4">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-t border-white/20 pt-4">
            <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[#A0A0A0]">Friction</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium">Moderate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-t border-white/20 pt-4">
            <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[#A0A0A0]">Car Access</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium">Nearby / Drop-off</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Model 3 */}
      <div class="border border-[#E5E5E5] bg-white p-8 flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <Car class="w-6 h-6 text-[#1A1A1A] mb-4" strokeWidth={1.5} />
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2">Countryside Edge</h3>
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm">Space and ease, but disconnected from the core.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto space-y-4">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-t border-[#E5E5E5] pt-4">
            <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[#666]">Friction</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium">Low</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-t border-[#E5E5E5] pt-4">
            <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[#666]">Car Access</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium">Direct</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 5. FIT / NOT FIT (SPLIT DECISION) */}
  <section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 border border-[#E5E5E5] bg-white">
      
      {/* Fit */}
      <div class="p-8 md:p-16 border-b lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-[#E5E5E5]">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-8">Frigiliana fits well if...</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1A1A1A] shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium mb-1">Atmosphere is your priority</div>
              <div class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm">You value historic charm over absolute logistical perfection.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1A1A1A] shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium mb-1">You don't mind walking</div>
              <div class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm">A 5-10 minute walk from car to door feels acceptable to you.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <Check class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1A1A1A] shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium mb-1">You prefer calm evenings</div>
              <div class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light text-sm">You want to be based where you dine and relax, driving mainly for day trips.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      {/* Not Fit */}
      <div class="p-8 md:p-16 bg-[#F9F8F6]">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-8 text-[#666]">Consider the coast if...</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <X class="w-5 h-5 text-[#666] shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium text-[#666] mb-1">You need zero-friction access</div>
              <div class="text-[#888] font-light text-sm">You want to park directly outside your front door every time.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <X class="w-5 h-5 text-[#666] shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium text-[#666] mb-1">Mobility is a concern</div>
              <div class="text-[#888] font-light text-sm">Steep inclines or stairs present a physical challenge for your group.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <X class="w-5 h-5 text-[#666] shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-medium text-[#666] mb-1">You are beach-obsessed</div>
              <div class="text-[#888] font-light text-sm">You plan to drive to the beach multiple times a day.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  {/* 6. AMARA ADVISORY (NEXT STEP) */}
  <section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto mb-12">
    <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] text-white p-8 md:p-16 text-center">
      <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-[#A0A0A0] mb-6 block">
        The AMARA Approach
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight">
        We select stays that balance village charm with manageable daily movement.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#A0A0A0] font-light text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        If you want the beauty of Frigiliana without the extreme logistical friction, explore our curated collection in the lower village.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="#explore" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#1A1A1A] text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
          Explore AMARA Stays
          <ArrowRight class="w-4 h-4" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>
